N.Y. Comp. Codes R. & Regs. Tit. 6 ยง 367.14 - Local beverage container laws

State Regulations

The provisions of this Part supersede any local beverage
container control laws which may be in effect on the effective date of this

Part. No such local laws may be enacted, implemented or enforced after the
effective date of this Part. Notes
